with the axe.

490
00:51:04,952 --> 00:51:07,810
No, you can't see me
'cause I'm a ghost.

491
00:51:07,862 --> 00:51:10,308
And ghosts are spirits
without bodies.

492
00:51:10,360 --> 00:51:12,753
- How do you know that?
- Sunday school.

493
00:51:14,339 --> 00:51:16,217
Hey, don't get too close.

494
00:51:16,301 --> 00:51:18,803
Nah, you can't hurt ghosts.

495
00:51:22,559 --> 00:51:24,958
