Sylvester, look!

496
00:51:25,010 --> 00:51:27,080
Maybe the Indians
took Nick,

497
00:51:27,132 --> 00:51:29,099
and they dropped it here.

498
00:51:29,151 --> 00:51:31,654
Nah, I think
he just ran away.

499
00:51:31,706 --> 00:51:34,106
Do you think
he'll ever come home?

500
00:51:34,158 --> 00:51:37,370
- He might be dead.
- Shut up, Jake, just shut up!

501
00:51:38,330 --> 00:51:41,334
