You should be helping Ma.

502
00:51:41,386 --> 00:51:43,962
I turned into a ghost,
and floated out.

503
00:51:46,466 --> 00:51:48,844
Sylvester, look.

504
00:51:51,890 --> 00:51:53,809
Sylvester:
First of the season.

505
00:51:53,861 --> 00:51:55,728
Prissy: Yup.
First of the season.

506
00:51:57,105 --> 00:51:59,129
Winter's just around
the corner.

507
00:51:59,181 --> 00:52:01,152
Yup. Just around
the corner.

508
00:52:01,204 --> 00:52:03,264
Priscilla?
Priscilla?

509
00:52:03,316 --> 00:52:05,273
Don't let her see me.

510
00:52:05,325 --> 00:52:07,368
I thought no one
could see you.

511
00:52:07,420 --> 00:52:09,413
Mothers can see
everything.

512
00:52:09,497 --> 00:52:13,043
- Prissy, I can see you there.
- I told you.

513
00:52:13,095 --> 00:52:14,947
Come in this instant.

514
00:52:14,999 --> 00:52:16,799
Or you'll wish you had.

515
00:52:19,219 --> 00:52:21,179
Sure wish Nick was here.

516
00:52:32,152 --> 00:52:34,447
(wagon approaching)

517
00:52:43,501 --> 00:52:45,921
- Man: Where would you look?
- Everywhere.

518
00:52:45,973 --> 00:52:47,882
That's a lot
of territory to cover.

519
00:52:51,012 --> 00:52:53,463
Martha, your bread
is delicious.

520
00:52:53,515 --> 00:52:55,600
Let me pour you
some more Brigham tea.

521
00:52:58,021 --> 00:52:59,930
Man: How do you know
who took him?

522
00:52:59,982 --> 00:53:02,548
I think it was the Bannocks.
they're the only ones

523
00:53:02,600 --> 00:53:05,463
- who come down this far.
- Why the Bannocks? Why not

524
00:53:05,515 --> 00:53:08,326
the Gosiutes or the Utes
or the Crow or the Shoshone?

525
00:53:08,378 --> 00:53:09,786
they were the first ones
I thought of.

526
00:53:09,911 --> 00:53:12,623
- I have to start somewhere.
- And how do you know

527
00:53:12,675 --> 00:53:14,449
they're not going
to take you?

528
00:53:14,501 --> 00:53:17,714
Or worse, kill you?
Will that help your mother?

529
00:53:17,766 --> 00:53:21,260
Good heavens, boy,
you're a farmer.

530
00:53:21,312 --> 00:53:23,712
You'd be eaten alive
up there.

531
00:53:23,764 --> 00:53:27,936
If not by savages, then
by the bear or mountain lion,

532
00:53:27,988 --> 00:53:30,214
- or by the elements.
- I gotta try.

533
00:53:30,266 --> 00:53:32,442
Don't you understand?
I gotta try.

534
00:53:32,525 --> 00:53:34,820
Can't you wait until
your father comes back?

535
00:53:34,945 --> 00:53:36,719
It'll be too late then.

536
00:53:36,771 --> 00:53:38,492
You think Nick's dead.

