01:01:23,160 --> 01:01:28,918
- Haata.
- Haata? Poisoned?

635
01:01:38,305 --> 01:01:41,935
- What did he say?
- He want you.

636
01:01:44,355 --> 01:01:49,987
White men trade maybe four,
five horses for you.

637
01:01:53,116 --> 01:01:55,703
Good price.

