01:03:29,288 --> 01:03:31,196
Sylvester: " Dearest Mother,

639
01:03:31,248 --> 01:03:35,171
once again, I'm afraid there is
no good news to tell you.

640
01:03:35,223 --> 01:03:39,093
I have followed many leads,
but still have no sign of Nick.

641
01:03:39,145 --> 01:03:40,793
It is September now.

642
01:03:40,845 --> 01:03:42,879
I will soon
have to make a choice,

643
01:03:42,931 --> 01:03:46,123
to come home,
or endure another winter.

644
01:03:46,175 --> 01:03:49,205
I wish you could advise me
what to do.

645
01:03:49,257 --> 01:03:52,236
I will write again
as soon as I can.

646
01:03:52,288 --> 01:03:53,987
Send everybody my love,

647
01:03:54,113 --> 01:03:56,074
and tell them
not to worry about me.

648
01:03:56,126 --> 01:03:58,077
I'm doing fine.

649
01:03:58,160 --> 01:04:00,246
Your loving son,
Sylvester."

650
01:04:00,298 --> 01:04:02,124
